description:
Lots of Bravo to discuss this week! Adam Salandra joins the show to breakdown the #RHONY finale, the #RHOD premiere, plus we dip into #RHOP/#RHOC, Aretha Franklin/Divas Live 1998, Jennifer Love Hewitt's selfie tips, & lots more! PLUS, Rachel & Laurie from A&E's Born This Way call in. For the full Rachel & Laurie interview, go to EverythingIconic.com.


New episodes every Monday & Thursday!
